		{
			"type": "action",
			"name": "Wail",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "action"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>the Botchling can lets out a horrific wail. Any creature within 60ft that can hear the wail must attempt a @Check[will|dc:15|options:area-effect] Save. Once used, the bothcling can't use Wail again for [[/gmr 1d4 #Duration]]{1d4 rounds}.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The Creature isn't affected</p><p><strong>Success</strong> the Creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed 1} until the end of its next turn.</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> the Creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.dfCMdR4wnpbYNTix]{Stunned 1} and is Slowed 1 until the end of its next turn.</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> the Creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.dfCMdR4wnpbYNTix]{Stunned 2} and is Slowed 1 for two rounds.</p>",
					"gm": ""
				},
