		{
			"type": "action",
			"name": "Deathly Echoes",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "passive"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>Whenever the botchling's wail cooldown ends, the botchling attempts at a @Check[flat|dc:15]. if it suceeds, the botchling attracts a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.pathfinder-monster-core.N98ug9jQHqeFoK1N]{Ghost Commoner} or a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.pathfinder-monster-core.VotlWUsFKdOrHWF6]{Shadow}, that will attack whoever tries to harm the botchling.</p>",
