		{
			"type": "action",
			"name": "A Nameless Soul",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "passive"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>A botchling can be put to rest if their parents hold them in their hands (making the botchling @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.kWc1fhmv9LBiTuei]{Grabbed}) for at least 1 round, and gives it a name, before burying with the proper rituals. Attacking a botchling while it's grabbed in this situation will make the botchling aggressive and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.ud7gTLwPeklzYSXG]{Hostile} towards everyone, making it impossible to use again A Nameless Soul for 24 hours.</p>",
